<section>
    <h2>Features of Xsun Coin</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Limited supply of <strong>36,666 coins</strong> ensures rarity and value preservation.</li>
        <li><strong>Deflationary Mechanism:</strong> 1% burn on each transaction reduces supply, ensuring deflationary pressure until the supply reaches <strong>25,666 coins</strong>.</li>
        <li>Built on Binance Smart Chain for high efficiency and security.</li>
        <li>Integration plans with networks such as Near Protocol, ERC20, and Tron for greater flexibility.</li>
        <li>User-friendly mining via our Android app.</li>
        <li>Upcoming listings on major exchanges planned for <strong>2026</strong>.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

